<%= @p1 %> chose Scissors. <br>

Computer chose <%= @computer_attack_type %>.

<% if @computer_attack_type == 'Rock' %>
  <p>Computer won!</p>
<% elsif @computer_attack_type == 'Paper' %>
  <p><%= @p1 %> won!</p>
<% else %>
  <p>It's a draw</p>
<% end %>

